\left(1+\frac1{km}\right)^{km}\to e
k\to\infty
k
(1+x)^n> 1+nx
x>0,n\ge2
\left(1-\frac1m\right)^m\cdot e>1-\frac1m
 \left(1-\frac1m\right)^m\cdot e\approx\left(1-\frac1m\right)^m\left(1+\frac1{km}\right)^{km}= \left[\left(1-\frac1m\right)\left(1+\frac1{km}\right)^k\right]^m
 \left[\left(1-\frac1m\right)\left(1+\frac1{km}\right)^k\right]^m> \left[\left(1-\frac1m\right)\left(1+\frac1{m}\right)\right]^m=\left(1-\frac1{m^2}\right)^m>1-\frac1m.
 \frac1e-\left(1-\frac1m\right)^m<\frac1{em}.
